Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:09.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗  把我叫来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:15.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把你的力量借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你居然会寻求借助别人的力量  这可太少见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别看我这样  我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然很抱歉  但还是另请高明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:29.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再稍微努力一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:11.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,漫画？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,近期会有一场同人展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我准备在那里出本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你吗  你来画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:25.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泷谷说上一次是纯文字的  所以肯定卖不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以这次要加上画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,难怪要画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是说到底  你为什么要出本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为了财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:34.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,财宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是某天发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:42.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫君  不是最喜欢财宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你有没有兴趣自己去创造财宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自己创造？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当自己创作了什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:57.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那将成为自己最珍贵的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你才会想出本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你找我就是想我帮你这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你早这么说就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  这忙我帮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那需要我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,填色还是排线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:15.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你很懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:22.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种本子里必须有色情又下流的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一起玩网游的家伙们是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:27.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我要你当我的绘画模特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,绘画模特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有点紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不对  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得我是下流的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:41.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我觉得没有比你更合适的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然说这么直白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是故事大纲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,登场人物是小学男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和年长的大姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就像我和翔太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等一下  你想对我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,撕开衣服舔遍全身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:03.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你写的什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个女人好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这男孩太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是接下来才是正题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从这里开始萌生爱意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可恶  那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很在意  那个人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是这样啊  我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我想咒死那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:31.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要诅咒那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,诅咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不允许你继续存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,诅咒你  诅咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个  法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这页之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是少年一直用各种咒术诅咒那个女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就是想表达这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:55.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类能理解你的感性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  我要画草稿了  你摆个姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好  之后是被诅咒时的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种的也要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:21.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就是为了这个才向你低头求助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有低头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是什么  你在耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,眼里流下血来  然后脖子转个360度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要到这种地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只有你才能做到如此精细的动作了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这种信赖太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真好  不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之后是让手飞速旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,用力折断之后飞向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,胸部和屁股分成三块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然很简单啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:57.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,接下来是腰  反身下腰然后像拱桥一样下楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有好好画下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么你要摆出一副绝望的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫君  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你还在画本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样  有进展了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也要加油赶稿出展了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他上次也卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我绝对不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说起来还没给你报酬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就随便给你一些我的财宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可不要被诅咒的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比起这个我也想出本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,借你的摊位给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以是可以  你要出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我的cosplay写真集之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨蛋  那种东西卖不掉的
