Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.75,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HF278F5&\bord5\b1\shad0\frz356\pos(366.286,878.047)}蜜 瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.25,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(547.429,650.286)}丰满与偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,偶尔参加这种活动也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看在我帮了你忙的份上  能给我一本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经寄到你家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太下流了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个下流的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,又把这种下流的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么能又一次被这种东西诱惑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,恶魔退散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,工…工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天是休息日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.99,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像刚从战场回来的战士一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:45.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天气这么好的话  能睡得很熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔不会觉得困吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龙一般不需要睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫纳为了守护财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是几万年不眠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这安保系统还真够持久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过我在寒冷的时候也会困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,类似冬眠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:09.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是呢  一般会就这样陷入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种时候如果没有特殊情况就醒不过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:14.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,特殊情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:17.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比如世界充满恶意时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:22.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,或是大地沾染血腥  化作瘴气发出腐烂的臭味时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,叫醒你的方式都显得非常不详
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,即使是这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来到这个世界之后也能安睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在配合我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然也有这方面的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但主要是不知觉间就产生了睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我倒是知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说到睡觉的话  就想到康娜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在也在睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好啦  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她们有自己的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明在那边睡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为她们以前没能和父母一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在跟小林你撒娇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊  托尔不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我以前经常和父母撒娇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吧  该睡回笼觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡觉很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那样子的小林是叫不醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没办法  出来买晚饭的食材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种时候看到你  真不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是我想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你买这么多甜食是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不如别当龙了  当头猪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡太久脑筋转不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也开始睡觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在学习人类的生活方式的过程中自然变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,过来这个世界以后  每晚都有睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,难道你也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:06.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这睡意是从何而来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,难道不是因为无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:10.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无聊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你觉得无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那为什么不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不讨厌无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:23.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们以前也试过不眠不休地战斗了好几年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当时可不无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:31.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们应该享受这份无聊啊  艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔  你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃了睡睡了吃的猪应该听不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,努力让你在肉店能以100克88日元卖掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别把我比作这种廉价的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在是人们睡觉的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能感觉到大部分的人类都在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无论往哪里看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,视野内的大部分人类都在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:23.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是在眺望安心睡觉的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡前一瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,白天睡太多了  晚上睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  人为什么会困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是生理现象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不睡觉就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也有一种说法是  在进化过程中没有选择夜行性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而选择了昼行性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来不是想听这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:58.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能是因为集体同步压力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是随波逐流的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:04.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:10.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从一开始有人说晚上太黑不好干活要早点睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后就有其他人认可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,说「我也是我也是」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在大家都去睡觉以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只剩自己一个人醒着有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就配合大家一起睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多就这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个说法满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,满意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:37.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也屈服于集体同步压力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.99,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}一般常识（大家都没有）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:13.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这次大家分小组调查  做一份手抄报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么大家互相讨论决定主题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们调查幽灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最近很多人都在聊这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从美术室仓库里传出女性的悲鸣声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,应该很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也觉得这个好  像是熊灵祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.93,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：熊灵祭，阿依努人传统信仰仪式，相信杀死棕熊能让其神灵回归天界。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行啊  康娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,世界上是没有幽灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,言之有理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以有关幽灵的传闻都毫无根据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么嘛  黑田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别…别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你个书呆子  书呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,反正你们就是害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么可能害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:54.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为了证明  我可以跟你们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看在康娜同学的面子上  我也不是不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好  那么就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是出现幽灵了的话就打飞她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幽灵没有实体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也摸不着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:18.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你一直都是太拘谨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以拍得到幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想拍幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为要是发到网上去不是会很火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:27.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,火？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是有很多点赞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总之我们先拍一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喂  还要不要调查幽灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没关系吧  就玩一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算上仓本  重头开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我明明都赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那最先到达终点的人就是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,队长的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川肯定是当仆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,仆人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你这个大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同学  要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定要给他们点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是康娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:19.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,第一名是康娜同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,往后对于康娜同学的命令要绝对服从
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快发号施令吧  康娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那家伙最近挺魔怔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们用这个踢球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蜂须贺  你够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,附带惩罚怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男生和女生踢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,输的一方要说出喜欢的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这根本不算惩罚好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我对康娜同学一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你难道不想知道小林同学喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要和才川结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蜂须贺  你这点子真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  那么开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,犯规了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,射门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要为了听到康娜同学的求婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我甘当小早川秀秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.91,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：小早川秀秋，日本战国时代末期大名，以关原之战中阵前倒戈的行为而闻名。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,成功策反
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是小林同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:50.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,偶尔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,哪里飞来的水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:55.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,战略性撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.76,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6396A6&\fs70\pos(998.667,504.333)}美 术 室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可饶不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完蛋  被看到脸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然这么胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:12.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,高年级也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,踢足球很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以后多踢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从美术室仓库里传出的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,传闻中的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那才川你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:42.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们是同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在刚才背叛了你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那还不是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同学  我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来是因为这个窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看  我不是说过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幽灵什么的都是无稽之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么嘛真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原本还想拍张幽灵的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,手抄报该怎么写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就写幽灵的真相其实是木制旋转窗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那样不是很没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把文章写得悬疑刺激点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不能胡编乱造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:51.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同学  我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是幽灵的传闻  好像已经传开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是从那边的世界来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错  是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是意外来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在那里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:16.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个地方是很好的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个声音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我在用那个黑色的板子磨指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:27.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但你能混在人类中生活好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:29.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类有很多无法理解的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,您很喜欢人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还是迫切地想回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,却对此束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道回到那个世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个好累的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这份恩情终生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不我们下次还是调查外星人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,昨天被你坑得这么惨  你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也有根有据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,照片也能火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的不想跟你们疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:31.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等下  康娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  就决定是这个了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天放学后去街上调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川答应晚了  所以负责背行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,凭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会背康娜同学的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:48.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但你的我不会背
Comment: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,---ED---
